    "Body": " Business Developer SwissBorg - Remote Apply Now Job Details Full-timeEstimated: $84,000 - $110,000 a year Qualifications Communication Skills Upselling Full Job Description Headquartered in Switzerland with additional offices in Toronto, London and soon in Tallinn, SwissBorg aims to fundamentally change the way individuals manage their wealth. As a product obsessed team, we believe that advanced technology combined with an intuitive user experience will empower people to invest with more freedom, confidence, and belief. In 2018, we successfully raised funds from over 23,800 global participants who share our vision of a wealth management industry with more community-centric values. We are now working towards the next phase of disruption. In 2020, individuals across the globe will have the opportunity to purchase digital assets such as Bitcoin at the best prices, and become members of our ecosystem to unlock first of its kind investment features. Due to the growth of our business, SwissBorg is offering an opportunity for a Business Developer to join our team in Tallinn, or to work remotely. If you are motivated, hardworking and want to participate in the new financial era, it is your chance to apply! Please note that you must be comfortable working in the EU time zone! What you'll be doing: Driving business growth by closing sales over the phone (40 per day) from leads delivered via pre-qualified marketing channels Establishing and maintaining customer relationships to improve cross-selling and up-selling opportunities from existing community members Sending marketing material to potential and existing investors Identifying and qualifying suitable investors Maintaining client relationships offering regular updates about their existing product and providing industry related news Increasing the investor\u2019s investment with the company and generating repeat business Motivating and monitoring the ambassador program and junior sales team on their fixed KPI metrics, etc Willing and able to regular the company\u2019s CRM system and overseeing the whole sales cycle Keeping up to date with industry related news. What you'll need: You're interested in Blockchain technology and cryptocurrencies You are street smart and college educated You have excellent English communication skills You are energetic, enthusiastic, and you love connecting and sharing ideas with others You have a track record of raising assets and selling products to Angel and institutional investors You have PR connections (media, influencers, business owners, etc...) What we offer: Being part of the lifetime opportunity to revolutionise the industry Get in on the ground floor as a pioneer in the fast paced fintech/blockchain space Salary and competitive bonus based on our meritocratic system Continuous opportunities to learn, grow fast, and create alongside an experienced team of financial experts, engineers, scientists, designers, and marketing gurus. ", 
